 <arm>
   <uof name="Topologically_Bounded_Surface">
     <description>
The Topologically_Bounded_Surface UoF specifies the data structure for the description of faces with fully defined geometry and explicit topology 
defining the boundaries. 
The covered types of face geometry include elementary surfaces and B-spline surfaces. 
Edges are required to have their geometry defined by curves, which may include pcurves.
     </description>
